1. *Prihvati* mi ponudu i mi ćemo postati najbolji prijatelji! (Accept my offer and we will become best friends!)

2. Ona je *prihvatila* poziv na večeru i otišla sa prijateljima. (She accepted the invitation to dinner and went with her friends.)

3. On je *prihvatio* da postane trener fudbalske ekipe. (He accepted to become a coach of the football team.)

4. *Prihvatili* smo njegovu ponudu i nastavili sa radom. (We accepted his offer and continued working.)

5. *Prihvatajući* njegovu ponudu, odlučila je da putuje. (Accepting his offer, she decided to travel.)